head of cattle. And the only way that I diagnosed it 
or knew what it was while I was I took one of the tags

09:17.412 --> 09:45.799
from a feed sack in his barn and I don't know I stuck 
it in my pocket and he had told me that his wife had

09:17.412 --> 09:45.799
never lost any hadn't lost any cattle with this and 
I said well how do you account for that he said I

09:17.412 --> 09:45.799
don't know but he said she won't buy she won't buy 
feed from the same people I buy from

