09:46.505 --> 10:12.124
that you're having losses from who are they buying 
their feed from and he's kind of hesitant to tell

09:46.505 --> 10:12.124
him And finally he told me who it was. I said, well, 
it's the same place mine's coming from. And that, I

10:17.586 --> 10:33.627
think, was to, as far as I was concerned, was the 
